---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Tam"
  description="Privacy policy for tam.buzz and Tam Philosophical Counseling."
>
  <main>
    <div class="py-20 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-lg uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-400/80 mb-4">
          tambuzztam LLC
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Effective date: March 20, 2026</p>

        <div
          class="prose prose-lg prose-invert prose-a:no-underline max-w-none"
        >
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            At tam.buzz, we are committed to maintaining the trust and
            confidence of visitors to our website and clients of Tam
            Philosophical Counseling.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Information we do not collect
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            tam.buzz does not collect personal information from visitors to our
            website. Our site is designed to provide information without
            requiring personal data. We do not keep records of names, email
            addresses, phone numbers, or any other personally identifiable
            information from casual visitors.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Counseling clients
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            When you schedule a session, your booking information is handled
            through our scheduling provider. We use that information solely to
            conduct and coordinate our work together. We are not in the business
            of selling, renting, or trading client information with any third
            party.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Session recordings and transcripts
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Sessions may be recorded (audio) or transcribed only with your prior
            written consent. No recording or transcription takes place without
            your explicit approval. Any recordings and transcripts are handled
            with care for your privacy and will not be shared with third parties
            without your consent.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Tracking &amp; cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We do not use cookies or any similar tracking technologies that
            monitor user behavior on our website.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Analytics
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            tam.buzz does not use analytics tools to monitor your behavior on
            our website. We value your privacy and are committed to not tracking
            your activity.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Third-party services
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            tam.buzz may contain links to third-party websites or services. We
            are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and
            encourage you to read their privacy statements when leaving ours.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We rely on industry best practices to secure our website, though no
            method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Changes to this policy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be
            posted on this page with an updated effective date.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Questions? Reach us at <a
              href="mailto:info@tam.buzz"
              class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 no-underline"
              >info@tam.buzz</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <a
            href="/#cta"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 no-underline transition-colors"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
            </svg>
            Back to Tam
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  html {
    scroll-snap-type: none;
  }
</style>
